00:08:34.770 --> 00:08:39.510
prepared and you just change them up a bit to answer the specific question.

135
00:08:39.510 --> 00:08:44.159
But deep down inside you're just demonstrating these qualities.

136
00:08:44.190 --> 00:08:50.700
Remember, these qualities are the qualities that we have to answer the last two questions, and that

137
00:08:50.700 --> 00:08:54.390
